comments: Rozier (CHA) and Powell (DAL) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact to Jackson's (DAL) arm off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Zeller (CHA) briefly grasps Finney-Smith's (DAL) arm during the pick but he immediately removes that hand.
Powell (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position along Graham's (CHA) path and he does not deliver the body contact on his shot attempt.
Zeller (CHA) makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) face/head during his pass attempt.
Rozier (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on Doncic (DAL) during his dribble.
Zeller (CHA) exits the paint within three seconds.
After the steal, Powell (DAL) swipes down and makes contact to the ball, any additional contact with Bridges' (CHA) arm is deemed incidental.
Powell (DAL) and Zeller (CHA) mutually engage in marginal arm contact prior to separating during the rebound.
Washington (CHA) slightly extends his forearm into Kleber's (DAL) front but the marginal contact does not affect Kleber's ability to defend the driving shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) exits the paint within three seconds.
Washington's (CHA) arm collapses to his body and he absorbs the oncoming body contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) during the pick.
Rozier (CHA) slightly extends his arm and initiates some contact to Doncic's (DAL) leg during the drive but the contact is marginal.

Powell (DAL) leaves the floor and absorbs the oncoming body contact with Rozier (CHA) during his driving shot attempt. Although Powell's arms are not perfectly vertical, he does not make contact to Rozier's arms.
Washington (CHA) exits the paint within three seconds.
Curry (DAL) briefly brings two hands to the ball and fumbles it as he attempts to gather at the end of the drive, Curry then legally regains possession of the ball to pass.
Bridges (CHA) makes "high-five" contact with Doncic (DAL) after the release of the ball during his jump shot attempt.
Rozier (CHA) delivers contact to Doncic's (DAL) body during the upward shooting motion and the contact affects his shot attempt.

Finney-Smith (DAL) makes some contact to Graham's (CHA) arm as he gathers the ball but the marginal contact does not affect his driving shot attempt. Graham's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Kleber (DAL) makes marginal contact to Washington's (CHA) arm that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Bridges' (CHA) heel hovers over the line but he does not step out of bounds at the start of his drive.
Doncic (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Bridges (CHA) during the drive.
Biyombo (CHA) exits the paint within three seconds.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes contact to Graham's (CHA) arm that affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Powell (DAL) commits a take foul on Bridges (CHA).
Biyombo (CHA) places two hands on Curry (DAL) during his dribble.
Finney-Smith (DAL) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Biyombo (CHA) commits a take foul on Curry (DAL).
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Graham (CHA).
Biyombo (CHA) briefly places a hand on Doncic's (DAL) body and removes it during his shot attempt.
